data.title: Who is AnnaLee Talley? — AnnaLee Talley & Purrbox
data.meta_description: Anna's a singer, songwriter & guitarist from Vero Beach, FL. She plays solo and with Will Keehner, her husband, on bass as the 'Anna & Will' duo. They're also both long-time, staple members in the local band Souljam.
data.text:
Nice to meet ya!

My name’s AnnaLee Talley Keehner ––Anna for short!

Get to know me!

I began my musical journey in south Georgia playing music in our local church and with my family.

After moving to Vero Beach, I attended Indian River Charter High School and excelled in the Visual & Performing Arts Program, which propelled me to start playing shows right after graduating in 2010.

After marrying my high school sweetheart in 2012, I officially and happily became AnnaLee Keehner. Coming from such a strong musical background, I decided to continue my solo music career using my maiden name, Talley. As a full time musician, I not only play solo shows but I also play with my husband in our duo, Purrbox along with being the staple members in the band Souljam for 9 years.

What does she sound like?

I’m so glad you asked!

After many years of performing, my list and genres of songs have grown to entertain a diverse crowd. Expect to hear original songs and tunes from the 60’s, 70’s, 80’s, and 90’s with songs of today sprinkled in between. I love playing music of all genres such as classic rock, funk, country, reggae, pop, jam, bluegrass, and many more. My sound is percussive and gives an energetic feel along with a soft soulful side.
